{"tid":697474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冇死人嘅所謂暴動就囚7年，施君龍燒死人最終囚5年仲畀移民香港","createTime":"2018-06-11T03:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T07:07:27.000Z","uid":40819,"like":27,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"edc1aacd73074184deff1f9b00b28028facc159e","tid":697474,"uid":40819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:49:01.000Z","msg":"燒死入境職員嘅施君龍，最終都係囚咗5年兼獲移民香港，呢個係咩天理呀？<br />\n<br />\nFrom wiki:<br />\n<br />\n施君龍為2000年入境事務大樓縱火案這宗恐怖襲擊之主犯，其後被判處謀殺罪成，判刑終身監禁，後來改判誤殺罪成，判刑監禁8年。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">他於05年獲釋後被即時遣返回大陸，於2011年成功申請單程證再來香港</span></strong>。"},{"pid":"2d4f33bc1d7f865d7a1e6590e87175c6f61a8aa8","tid":697474,"uid":61280,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T03:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">67班共狗就年年銷遙法外，清明拉大隊警犬仲幫手開路！！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb6073bf9f4c17bfdefdb127bc4a81d18274450c","tid":697474,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:00:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"804a67203567ba2dd27bba8130b18996fe6a5319","tid":697474,"uid":31907,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:01:03.000Z","msg":"集氣叫美國人出手啦，代價係香港D美債/美金儲備送返比美國，加入合眾國，䄲稅比美國"},{"pid":"d93190f4a28ae334ca94ad141acba35194be544f","tid":697474,"uid":65074,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:04:12.000Z","msg":"預告： <br />\nd五毛首先會話天琦抵死<br />\n之後會問你鍵盤戰士不了要返工<br />\n之後會狂推其他膠post洗板"},{"pid":"b6aae204f4b6dcc77ba7fe78e546f540be57ae9d","tid":697474,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T04:06:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8084230a499c4b15fc046ac4966d